{"type":"message","id":"371e519d","parentId":"1657103b","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:35:59.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the image analysis is failing because the MiniMax model doesn't seem to support image input in this configuration. Let me just ask the user to describe the platform they're referring to, since I can't see the image. Or wait - maybe I can use a different approach.\n\nActually, looking at the image again - the user says \"上次用这个做了几次调试，8次就没了\" - meaning \"I've used this for debugging a few times, and it was gone after 8 times.\" This sounds like a platform with limited free credits - possibly an AI API platform with only 8 free calls.\n\nAnd they mention \"选品\" (product selection) - this sounds like they want to use this platform for AI-assisted product selection for e-commerce.\n\nLet me ask the user to describe what platform is in the image since I can't see it.\n\nActually wait - the user sent an image that I can't analyze. Let me try describing what the image likely is based on the context:\n- They mentioned doing \"调试\" (debugging/testing) several times and it was gone after 8 uses\n- They want to use it for \"选品\" (product selection)\n- This sounds like it could be an AI platform with limited free credits\n\nCommon platforms for product selection with AI could include:\n- 1688-related AI tools\n- 抖音/小红书 related tools\n- Various AI API platforms\n\nSince I can't see the image, I should ask the user to describe what's in it. But let me try one more approach - maybe I can use exec to check image metadata or something.\n\nActually, I should just ask the user what platform is shown, since I cannot analyze the image. The image tool seems to have an issue with the MiniMax model configuration for image inputs.","thinkingSignature":"03a368fdd79f792dde121c86c36bc87914be2460ced3f2b2afa542d6dfb9bec5"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，图片分析功能目前有点问题，我无法看到你分享的截图。能麻烦你简单描述一下这个平台吗？比如：\n\n- 这是什么平台/服务？（名字）\n- 主要是做什么功能的？\n- 