{"type":"message","id":"99d9c116","parentId":"43bc70e1","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:36:45.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they understand what I was trying to say (about the image analysis issue) and is now talking about \"3万次\" (30,000 times) being enough for their use. They're talking about usage quotas - seems like this is about an API or service they want to use for product selection (选品).\n\nFrom context, they seem to be evaluating whether some platform's quota of 30,000 uses would be sufficient for their product selection work. The previous message mentioned doing \"8次\" (8 times) of debugging and hitting a limit.\n\nI don't have the image context, but based on the conversation flow, they're evaluating a platform (probably some kind of AI/LLM API service) for product selection purposes. They're asking if 30,000 uses would be enough.\n\n\nSo the key question is whether that volume is sufficient for their needs, but I don't have enough information about their typical usage patterns or the scale of their product selection work to give a confident answer. I'm not entirely sure which specific platform or service they're referring to without seeing the image, but based on the conversation context about debugging and usage limits, I can provide general guidance on whether 30,000 uses would be sufficient for their product selection needs.","thinkingSignature":"8b32179e6bb1184b963fb0085685badd126ec558472aea24ed5be06264d3d7f6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n3万次的话，基本够用了——看你选品规模多大。\n\n如果你们是小批量测品、慢慢筛，3万次撑几个月没问题。但如果是高频调用、批量跑，几下就没了。\n\n你们打算怎么用？是：\n- **每次选品都调API**（高频）\n- 还是**偶尔查一下**（低频）\n\n这个决定了够不够用。另外你说的\"8次就没了\"是调了8次就没额度了，还是其他意思？我理解一下场景，帮你判断。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18197,"output":357,"cacheRead":96,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778225786414,