{"type":"message","id":"a3ebde21","parentId":"d0984d50","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:40:30.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace is quite bare - only basic AGENTS.md skeleton files. Let me ask about the key missing pieces. I need to understand:\n\n1. What is the 5.0 documentation referring to?\n2. What is the selection (选品) workflow?\n3. What platform are we using?\n\nLet me ask targeted questions to move forward.","thinkingSignature":"ab9f460443fa741c4a9b3e9615d244001d89dae492e46f1b22c3a448e670219e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nworkspace 目前只有基础框架，没有实际项目内容。几个关键问题需要你先回答，我才能开始搭：\n\n**1. 选品 SOP 相关**\n- 选品流程是什么？比如：输入商品链接/关键词 → 调用 AI 分析 → 输出评分/推荐？\n- 有没有现有的操作流程文档，或者你是怎么做的？\n- 判断标准是什么？（销量、市场需求、竞争度？）\n\n**2. 5.0 文档**\n- 你说的 5.0 版本文档是什么？我没有看到 workspace 里有。\n- 是某个平台的使用手册？还是 AI Agent 相关的教程？\n\n**3. 平台**\n- 是调用哪个 AI API？MiniMax 还是其他？\n- 调用方式是什么？（REST API？SDK？）\n- 3万次额度大概能支撑多大调用量？\n\n**4. 最终输出**\n- 选品结果以什么形式交付？（表格？报告？）\n- 需要我帮写代码/脚本吗？\n\n你现在能直接回答最好，这样我马上开始写 SOP 和配置文档，不用反复确认。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":551,"output":281,"cacheRead":18944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778226024771,"responseId":"064cc6684b1fad4e94ca646cc28b94e7"}}
