{"type":"message","id":"865f4245","parentId":"7f55c46b","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:49:15.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to organize what we need to do and complete all configuration tomorrow. Let me think about what needs to be done:\n\n1. **Documentation (ongoing)**:\n   - SOP.md - ✅ DONE\n   - AGENTS.md - needs to be updated with TTS agent identity and configuration\n   - SOUL.md - needs to be configured for the TTS (选品) agent persona\n   - TOOLS.md - needs to specify tools, API keys, platform details\n   - USER.md - needs to be filled with user information\n   - IDENTITY.md - needs to be filled with agent identity\n\n2. **选品 Platform**:\n   - User mentioned a platform with 3万次 quota that ran out after 8 times\n   - I couldn't see the image, so I don't know exactly which platform\n   - Need to clarify\n\n3. **Agent Configuration**:\n   - The agent workspace is at /home/halei/workspace-tts\n   - We need to configure it properly as a TTS (TikTok Shop Sourcing) agent\n   - Need to set up the feishu channel integration\n\n4. **Bitable Integration**:\n   - App Token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n   - Table ID: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n   - This needs to be configured for product sourcing workflow\n\n5. **What needs to be done**:\n   - Complete IDENTITY.md (name, nature, vibe, emoji)\n   - Complete USER.md (user info)\n   - Complete TOOLS.md (TTS specific tools, API keys, platform)\n   - Update AGENTS.md with proper TTS agent configuration\n   - Update SOUL.md with persona for a sourcing agent\n   - Set up the workflow for daily sourcing operations\n   - Configure the Bitable tool for writing products\n   - Integrate the feishu-doc skill properly\n\nNow I should organize this into a clear action plan for tomorrow's configuration work.","thinkingSignature":"3f3f80710e2f924c55733e0f0a6713f5cd338b9d6c8f5a8749d3020298baa74c"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我梳理一下要做的事情，按优先级分：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 TTS 选品 Agent 配置清单\n\n### 一、文档补全（今天已完成）\n- ✅ SOP.md - 选品方法论 v5.0\n- ⬜ IDENTITY.md - 身份配置\n- ⬜ USER.md - 用户信息\n- ⬜ TOOLS.md - 工具配置\n- ⬜ AGENTS.md - Agent 配置\n- ⬜ SOUL.md - 人格配置\n\n### 二、明天要配的核心内容\n\n| 序号 | 事项 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|-----|------|------|------|\n| 1 | **Agent 身份** - 命名、定位、人格 | 待确认 | 你来定 |\n| 2 | **选品平台** - 哪个平台？API 接哪家？ | 待确认 | 图片看不到，你描述一下 |\n| 3 | **Bitable 写入** - 飞书多维表自动同步 | 待配 | Token 已拿到 |\n| 4 | **Feishu 文档读写** - SOP 落地到飞书 | 待配 | 已能访问 |\n| 5 | **日/周报推送** - 自动汇报选品结果 | 待设计 | 推送频率和格式 |\n| 6 | **数据源** - EchoTik/1688/其他 | 待确认 | 哪些数据源要接 |\n| 7 | **API 额度** - 3万次怎么用、怎么省 | 待规划 | 8次就没了说明调用方式有问题 |\n\n### 三、缺失的关键信息\n\n**需要你确认：**\n\n1. **选品平台** —— 你发的截图是什么平台？我看不到图片，描述一下？\n   - 是 MiniMax？\n   - 还是其他 AI API 平台？\n   - 调用方式是 REST API 还是 SDK？\n\n2. **Agent 身份** —— 我应该叫什么？\n   - 名字？\n   - 是 AI 选品助手？选品大师？供应链顾问？\n\n3. **每天/每周要输出什么？**\n   - 选品报告推送到哪里？（飞书群？私聊？）\n   - 推送频率？（每天早上10点？每周一？）\n   - 格式？（多维表链接？摘要文字？）\n\n4. **数据源优先级**\n   - EchoTik（数据平台）\n   - 1688（货源）\n   - TikTok Shop 后台\n   - 其他？\n\n---\n\n**你先回答上面几个问题，明天我全部配完。**\n\n回答完我马上开始干活，今天先把能做的文档框架做好。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":135,"output":959,"cacheRead":16540,"cacheWrite":42836,"totalTokens":60470,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778226525944,"responseId":"064cc85e1f611472ba13ae853ebf7ed4"}}
