{"type":"message","id":"efbe76a2","parentId":"ad9cbc38","timestamp":"2026-05-08T08:10:59.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about two approaches:\n1. Sorftime MCP - just need to recharge to get it working\n2. Browser automation using CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) to drive Chrome on their computer\n\nThey want to know which approach I prefer.\n\nLet me think about this:\n\n**Sorftime MCP (Option 1):**\n- Pros: Direct API, structured data, reliable, no UI dependency\n- Cons: Need to recharge, still has 30k limit\n\n**CDP/Chrome native approach (Option 2):**\n- This would be using Playwright or similar with CDP to control Chrome\n- Pros: Can操作任何网站，包括需要登录的1688、EchoTik等\n- Cons: 需要Chrome运行在机器上，可能需要处理登录态、验证码等\n\nActually, I should ask - what exactly does \"CDP原生方式驱动chrome\" mean? Are they talking about using a tool like:\n- Playwright (which uses CDP)\n- Puppeteer\n- Selenium\n- Chrome DevTools Protocol directly\n\nAnd importantly - if Chrome is running on their machine, can I actually control it from this environment? There might be network/security restrictions.\n\nLet me think about which is better:\n1. Sorftime MCP is cleaner if it has the data we need\n2. CDP approach is more flexible but more complex\n\nActually, I think Sorftime MCP is the clear winner for the data source problem because:\n- It's an API, structured data\n- Reliable\n- No UI automation complexity\n- Just need to recharge\n\nThe CDP/browser approach would be:\n- More complex to set up\n- May have reliability issues (login sessions, etc.)\n- Better as a fallback\n\nSo I should recommend Sorftime MCP first, and mention that CDP approach is possible as a backup.\n\nBut wait - they said \" Sorftime MCP认证问题：key过期了。充值就可以用了\" - meaning Sorftime MCP just needs recharge to work. This is the simpler path.\n\n\nI should check if Playwright is available in this environment to understand what tools I actually have at my disposal for browser automation.","thinkingSignature":"5c6adc57baab4b0adc69c2512dcd868feb1f10f820192433e4d58022ba77f092"},{"type":"text","text":"**我更倾向 Sorftime MCP**，原因：\n\n| | Sorftime MCP | CDP 浏览器控制 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **稳定性** | API 调用，稳定可靠 | 浏览器实例可能崩溃/掉线 |\n| **维护成本** | 几乎零维护 | 需要处理登录态、验证码、页面变化 |\n| **成功率** | 接近 100% | 依赖页面结构，可能翻车 |\n| **速度** | 快 | 慢（页面加载、渲染） |\n\n**CDP 方案适合作为补充**，比如：\n- Sorftime 没有的数据\n- 需要截图验证\n- 特殊页面结构\n\n---\n\n先充值 Sorftime，跑通用再说。CDP 留着当备选。\n\n充值好了告我，我马上测试 Sorftime MCP 能调出哪些数据。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":135,"output":590,"cacheRead":16540,"cacheWrite":35560,"totalTokens":52825,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778227836953,"responseId":"064ccd7d0a9426145a6a25dd199fd471"}}
