{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50ede2dde8a8c49e4215de09907\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-08 16:11 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"29665ae6","parentId":"62f86ef6","timestamp":"2026-05-08T08:11:49.385Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"20ffc3d0","parentId":"29665ae6","timestamp":"2026-05-08T08:12:01.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if 100 test calls are enough to get started. Let me think about this:\n\n1. Sorftime MCP has 100 test calls available\n2. We need to figure out what calls we need to make for the SOP\n\nLooking at the SOP, the key data points needed are:\n- 月销量 (monthly sales)\n- 评分数 (review count)\n- 上架时间 (listing time)\n- 客单价 (unit price)\n- 精准标签/Hashtag\n- 竞争对手 CPM data\n- 毛利计算\n\nThe user is saying they could register a new account to get more test calls. \n\n100 test calls is definitely workable for getting started. The user can register a fresh account to get 100 additional test calls, giving them 200 total to validate the workflow. But they also mentioned充值 (topping up) earlier, so I should clarify which approach they prefer—充值 their current account or registering a new one—since both are viable paths forward.","thinkingSignature":"2b3fbd173c535148a74c9a65301d3012650047cfb29a5177e611d834625b325d"},{"type":"text","text":"100次**绝对够用**，理由：\n\n1. **注册新账号 = 又是100次测试** → 两个账号加起来 200 次\n2. **先把流程跑通** → 选品 SOP 验证阶段不需要高频调用\n3. **跑通后再充值** → 心里有数，知道花的钱去哪了\n\n**建议：**\n- 新账号先跑 20-30 次，把核心功能测完\n- 充值之前告诉我，我帮你做个消耗评估，看 3 万次能用多久\n\n先注册吧，账号好了直接告我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":135,"output":323,"cacheRead":51842,"cacheWrite":487,"totalTokens":52787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778227909385,"responseId":"064ccdc64c70a087f8c9276100eba3ce"}}
